tagline: Chart results from multiple cross-account timeseries queries
details: This is a Custom Visualization that allows you to add the results of multiple cross-account timeseries queries to a single chart. The [current limit](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/query-your-data/explore-query-data/query-builder/use-advanced-nrql-mode-query-data/) in Newrelic One is 20 queries per chart, but this allows you to add many more.
